Hello Dan,
the kernel definitively supports transparent proxy.
You have to enable firewalling (CONFIG_IP_FIREWALL) _AND_ you
must always defragment a packet (CONFIG_IP_ALWAYS_DEFRAG) in your .config.
Regards
Frank Bernard
frankb@ipf.de
www.linux-firewall.de
